C     DOES NOT SIGNIFICANTLY PERTURB THE HSO4-SO4 EQUILIBRIUM. THE NITRIC
C     ACID DISSOLVED IS CALCULATED FROM THE HNO3(G) -> (H+) + (NO3-) 
